summary: This is my preset for Racemenu of Idunn, the Norse Goddess.
descriptionHtml:
This is my preset for Racemenu of Idunn, the Norse Goddess.

***REQUIRED MODS***

SKSE: [color=#0000ff][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]http://skse.silverlock.org/[/url][/color]
RaceMenu: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?[/url]
Ks Hairdo's Renewal: [color=#0000ff][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?[/url][/color]
Mikan Eyes: [color=#0000ff][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056/?[/url][/color]

***RECOMMENDED MODS***

KJ Tattoos - Overlay Plugins for RaceMenu: [color=#0000ff][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50032/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50032/?[/url][/color]
Triss' Dress: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67601/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67601/?
[/url]Remodeled Armor for CBBE Bodyslide HDT: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25259/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25259/?[/url]
Equipment Of Eternal Shine: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17582/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17582/?[/url]
These mods are shown in the screenshots.

Just need to put this .jslot file in your Skyrim folder (Data/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets).
In game, open RaceMenu and press F9 in the Presets option. Select "Idunn.jslot" one and enjoy!
Let me know if this preset doesn't work or having problems with it, it's my first mod :D
author: Hemidroid
